Full Description: The Film Society of Lincoln Center is a film presentation organization that celebrates American and international cinema; recognizes and supports new filmmakers; and enhances awareness, accessibility, and understanding of the art among a broad and diverse film going audience. The organization presents year-round programming that includes premieres of new films, major retrospectives, in-depth symposia, and high profile events. The Film Society of Lincoln Center is best known for two international festivals: the New York Film Festival, and New Directors/New Films. It runs two state-of-the-art year round cinemas: the Walter Reade Theater and the Elinor Bunin Munroe Film Center. Film Comment is a cinematic journal produced by the organization. Each year the organization presents its annual Gala Tribute honoring legendary stars and industry leaders at Lincoln Center’s Alice Tully Hall. At various times of the year the Film Society partners with Hollywood studios to present premieres and special live appearances. The organization is a supporter of the International Federation of Film Archives (FIAF). The Film Society of Lincoln Center was founded in 1969 and is based in New York, United States.

Description: Act Earth Wise is an active eco-conscious organization, consultancy and online retailer of products and services.
Headquarters Regions: Greater Seattle Area, West Coast, Western US
Full Description: Act Earth Wise, LLC is a hardware, software, and consulting services company focused on delivering carbon-neutral solutions for our customers. Every action we take as an organization must address one or more of the three pillars. First, does the solution drive a better outcome for our planet? Second,  does the solution reduce or eliminate the consumption of fossil fuels measurably? Third, can technology be applied to automate processes that eliminate human decision-making needs that impact sustainability and carbon-neutral outcomes?  We work with cities and municipalities, hospitals and clinics, schools and police departments, enterprises, and small businesses looking to develop safer, more efficient spaces for employees, guests, and customers.  Our medical-grade smart air purifiers, UV lighting solutions, and IOT sensors allow our customers to automate the management process of cleaning, sanitizing, and delivering the highest possible air quality within their facility. We team with third-party technology partners to implement and manage policies to support post-covid return to work and optimized hybrid work initiatives. Working with Operations and Facilities teams, we increase operation and energy efficiencies for our customers.    Our product brands include Earthwise UV (earthwiseuv.com), a product division that designs, builds, and OEMs hardware solutions that improve air quality and safely eliminate pathogens from surfaces.  Citicoco (citicoco.com) tackles the growing demand to return to work with fossil fuel-based vehicles with a line of personal and IOT-enabled eBikes and eScooters designed to support city-sharing programs globally.  Finally, Earth Wise Gifts (earthwisegifts.com) provides alternative products to plastic/petroleum-derived products. We focus on sustainable, reusable, renewable products and partnerships that align with our principles. Our Earth Wise Gifts team regularly engages with local communities to participate in beach clean-up, recycling, and charitable efforts.
